      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It's been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and you won't find a single scratch or dent on it. It drives like a dream and is ready for your next adventure! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
