      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band and razor-sharp throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in flawless condition, with no subframe fatigue and a suspension system that retains its original kinematic precision. This example boasts factory-spec paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship, including documented rod bearing and VANOS preventative maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
