      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive care and preservation. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been meticulously maintained with professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of stone chips, swirl marks, or dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear on the bolsters, while the carpets and headliner are pristine. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history from authorized dealerships. Every component, from the smooth-shifting transmission to the responsive infotainment system, functions perfectly. Always garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this single-owner vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 44900.0,
